data.description: This loan is assumable, ask listing agent for details. *If buyer uses Josh Penland at Fairway Mortgage, the lender will pay for a 1/0 temporary rate buydown. See attached flyer.* Stunning four bedroom, three bathroom home is designed with sleek finishes and an open floorplan. As you step into the home, you are greeted by a bright and airy living room. The windows allow for a seamless integration of the outdoors and indoors. The open kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances. The sparkling quartz countertops, complemented by a tile backsplash, provide ample space for meal preparation. The breakfast bar and island offer additional seating options, making it ideal for casual dining or gathering with friends and family. Adjacent to the kitchen is a cozy breakfast area, where you can enjoy your morning coffee while basking in the natural light. The primary suite is a spacious retreat, featuring plush carpets and a ceiling fan, this room offers a serene atmosphere for rest and rejuvenation. The ensuite bathroom boasts a walk-in shower, perfect for unwinding after a long day. The double vanity provides space for personal care items and the walk-in closet offers plenty of storage for your wardrobe. On the main level, you will find two additional bedrooms, each offering comfort and privacy. These rooms are serviced by a full bathroom, complete with a single vanity and a tub/shower combo. Upstairs, a versatile loft, full bedroom and bath area awaits, providing endless possibilities. Whether you envision it as a home office, a playroom, a media room, or a cozy reading nook, this space can be customized to suit your lifestyle and preferences. The open layout creates a seamless flow, allowing you to adapt the space to your specific needs. Outside, the home is surrounded by meticulously landscaped grounds, enhancing the curb appeal and creating a backyard tranquil outdoor oasis.
